Enum EDbVendor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EDbVendor>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<EDbVendor>

    public enum EDbVendor
extends Enum<EDbVendor>
    Database vendors supported:
    dbvmssql,dbvoracle,dbvmysql,dbvdb2, dbvsybase, dbvinformix,dbvpostgresql,dbvteradata, dbvmdx,dbvnetezza,dbvhive,dbvgreenplum,dbvredshift

    No specific engine for Microsoft ACCESS dbvaccess, use dbvmssql instead.

    Database engine not supported:
    dbvgeneric,dbvfirebird,dbvansi,dbvodbc
